node.text:
— GIVEAWAY CLOSED! Winners: @anitaaeo @_jmarieso @sarahbwrs @tiffany_maupin —

CHALLENGE GIVEAWAY 🥰 Ya know we had to!

On Thursday, 4 people will be chosen from comments to win. 2 will win a COACHED spot in the @fitbykaty #FBKCelebr8 Challenge & 2 will win an uncoached spot!

To enter, you must be following me & @fitbykaty - then, just comment below and tag a friend who you’d love to do this Challenge alongside 🖤 fitness is more fun with friends! Less than 2 weeks until Day 1! If you have questions on what all is included, cost etc, head over to @fitbykaty and check out the FBKCelebr8 highlight 🥳

node.text: freaking out for nothing 😜 it’s like you were born for this! these boys really did hit the dad lottery with you. you are patient, you love watching them learn and teaching them new things, and you get giggles out of them better than anyone can. we are so lucky you’re ours 🖤 happy Father’s Day! we love you!! @haydnschneider

node.text:
My two ☁️Keep It Dreamy☁️ campaign kits launch on @alaninutrition tomorrow ☮️ I’m giving three lucky ducks a chance to win it all! 3 of you will be selected to win the following:

No Bad Daze box
Good Vibes Only box
A CASE of both Energy flavors
+ every single iron on patch (you’ll be the only people with them all!)

All you have to do is be following me & AlaniNu, comment below a funny story about a trippy trip/vibey vibe you’ve had 😜 // if that isn’t your jam, just let me know how you keep the bad daze away & good vibes rolling!

lastly, a teensy note from me:
thank you to the moon for all the love you’ve sent for this campaign! it has been my absolute most most favorite project ever and I’m so happy you think it’s cool! one of the best parts about owning my own companies is getting to be creative with them.. and it’s alllllll in lighthearted, responsible fun! love u guys so big!
